<ansi fg="yellow-bold">combatinfo</ansi> - Show detailed combat calculations

<ansi fg="cyan">Usage:</ansi>
  combatinfo [target]

<ansi fg="cyan">Description:</ansi>
  Displays detailed combat information and calculations for a target character
  or mob. If no target is specified, shows information for yourself.

  This command shows:
  - Speed statistics and bonuses
  - Weapon information and cooldown calculations (twitch combat)
  - Attack intervals and weapon speeds (round-based combat)
  - All character stats
  - Active combat system information

<ansi fg="cyan">Examples:</ansi>
  combatinfo          - Show your own combat information
  combatinfo rat      - Show combat info for a rat
  combatinfo guard    - Show combat info for a guard

<ansi fg="cyan">Note:</ansi>
  This is an admin-only command used for debugging and understanding
  combat calculations.

<ansi fg="yellow">See Also:</ansi> attack, balance, consider